{"tid":1438370,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"大埔景點 - 香港回歸紀念塔","createTime":"2019-08-09T17:57:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-10T14:55:23.000Z","uid":112094,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"df05e8382ec0be4d337c01e7e0279508ffae5873","tid":1438370,"uid":112094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T17:57:41.000Z","msg":"香港回歸紀念塔是香港的一座紀念塔，位於新界大埔區大埔海濱公園之內，於1997年與公園同步開放，以紀念香港回歸。<br />\n<br />\n該塔高32.4米，塔下有碑記說明興建意義，大意是新界鄉民在<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港被割讓予英國初年保衛鄉土、壯烈犧牲；香港淪陷，鄉民對日抗戰；以至香港重光，新界發展，鄉民積極參與，作出重大的貢獻</span></span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rKYNW8J.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrKYNW8J.png&h=2af6968c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9762b0939dfa3bbcb79d357b2c5f5854b9da8a1f","tid":1438370,"uid":139611,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T14:55:23.000Z","msg":"形狀成舊屎咁 💩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}